      • isAutoArrange

        public boolean isAutoArrange()

      • setAutoArrange

        public void setAutoArrange(boolean autoArrange)
        Sets photo(s) arrangement in "Customize Product" screen.

        If value is set to true, instead of showing a blank product, images will be pre-arranged on it. The user will still be able to change the arrangement.

        If value is set to false, a dialog will appear allowing the user to choose between automatic and manual arrangement.
        Parameters:
        autoArrange - Flag telling if auto arrangement should be applied. Default value is false.

        public void setVendorLogoOnScreen(Screen screen,
                         java.lang.Integer resourceId)
        Sets drawable resource ID to be used as vendor logo for supplied Screen. By default, no screens have logo associated with them. Following screens have support for showing vendor logo: Screen.PAYMENT, Screen.ORDER_COMPLETED and Screen.PRODUCT_DETAILS.
        Parameters:
        screen - The screen where logo should be shown.
        resourceId - The logo drawable resource ID that will be asociated to the supplied screen. If null value is supplied vendor logo will be hidden.
